    "content": "<section class=\"section\">\n    <h2>문제 설명</h2>\n    <p>실수 <code>flo</code>가 <code>input()</code>으로 주어질 때, <strong>flo의 정수 부분</strong>만 출력하도록 코드를 작성하세요.</p>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"section\">\n    <h2>제한사항</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li><code>0 ≤ flo ≤ 100</code></li>\n      <li><code>input()</code> 함수 안에 문자열을 넣지 마세요. (예: <code>input(\"실수: \") ❌</code>)</li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"section\">\n    <h2>입출력 예</h2>\n    <table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"6\">\n      <thead style=\"background-color:#eee;\">\n        <tr><th>번호</th><th>flo</th><th>결과</th></tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr><td>1</td><td>\"1.42\"</td><td>1</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>2</td><td>\"69.32\"</td><td>69</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </section>",
